    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303670/extras/19cc893364ba570490b72a7a3ad97b19.poster.avif?t=1765826613\" width=1170 height=504 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303670/extras/19cc893364ba570490b72a7a3ad97b19.webm?t=1765826613\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303670/extras/19cc893364ba570490b72a7a3ad97b19.mp4?t=1765826613\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rewind back to 2004 and find out why so many students are going missing in the infamous Swiss boarding school of Noirmont High. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Choose a starting skill </strong>(you can be <i>perceptive</i>, <i>athletic</i> or <i>resourceful</i>)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Choose your fear</strong> (do you have <i>scary intrusive thoughts</i>, an <i>irrational fear of a duck watching you</i> or are you just <i>afraid people will notice you're stupid</i>?)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>And choose everything else!</strong> because it's a choice-matters game</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Investigate, explore... try not to be the next one</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move around in a 3D environment and interact with characters in 2D comic book panel, in this hybrid between visual novel and adventure game. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303670/extras/72b89819d4373f4a175417bba136dbf8.poster.avif?t=1765826613\" width=1170 height=504 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303670/extras/72b89819d4373f4a175417bba136dbf8.webm?t=1765826613\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303670/extras/72b89819d4373f4a175417bba136dbf8.mp4?t=1765826613\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features be like</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A cinematic experience</strong> with fully animated people and cool camera movements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mystery &amp; spooks</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hand-drawn comic-book panels</strong> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Nostalgic soundtrack </strong> by the artist Icarus</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>y2k vibe</strong> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>A spook-free mode</strong></u> if you don't like horror and still want to enjoy the story!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303670/extras/ba8abcaacde10aaa805ec688ed7eecf8.avif?t=1765826613\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303670/extras_big/ba8abcaacde10aaa805ec688ed7eecf8.webp?t=1765826613 width=1560 height=666 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
